$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT DV WTKG GENDER AGE RATE
$DATA      ..\..\datalarge.csv IGNORE=@
           
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN2 ;; advan2 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WTKG/70  ;; CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WTKG-70  ;; CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/40
;; thetas out of sequence
  TVV2=THETA(2)*CWTKGONE**THETA(4) *CWTKGONE**THETA(5)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2)) 
  TVCL= THETA(1) *EXP(CWTKGZERO*THETA(6))  *CAGE**THETA(7)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) 
  K=CL/V2 
  ;; thetas out of sequence here
  ;; PK 1 compartment  
    D1=THETA(8)  ; infusion only ; include D1 and lag, with diag or block OMEGA
  
  TVKA=THETA(3) 
  KA=TVKA    
  S2 	= V2/1000 
$ERROR     
 REP = IREP      
 IPRED =F  
 IOBS = F +EPS(1)
 Y=IOBS
$THETA  ;; must be one THETA per line.
 (0.001,100)	; THETA(1) CL UNITS =  L/HR
 (0.001,500) 	; THETA(2) V  UNITS = L
 (0.001,2) 	; THETA(3) KA UNITS = 1/HR 
;; test for comments in blocks
;; test for comments in blocks

 ;; THETA 1 compartment  ;; comment
   (-4,0.8,4) 	; THETA(4) POWER volume ~WT    ;;; comment ;; comment
   (-4,0.1,4) 	; THETA(5) POWER volume ~SEX    ;;; comment ;; comment
;; test for comments in blocks
   (-1,0.01,4) 	; THETA(6) EXPONENTIAL clearance~WT  
   (-4,-0.2,4) 	; THETA(7) POWER clearance~AGE  
   (0.01,0.2) 		;; D1 THETA 
$OMEGA   ;; must be one ETA/line
  0.2  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
$OMEGA
;; test for comments in blocks
  0.2 	; ETA(2) VOLUME
;; optional $OMEGA blocks
  
;; test for comments in blocks
 
 		;; D1 ETA only 
$SIGMA  
;; test for comments in blocks

  3000 	; EPS(1) additive error
$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E

  CWTKGONE = WTKG/70  ;; CENTERED ON ONE

  K32=THETA(5)
  K24=THETA(6)
  K42=THETA(7)

 IPRED =F  
 IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
 Y=IOBS

 (0.001,0.1) 	;; THETA(6) k24  
 (0.001,0.1) 	;; THETA(7)k42  
  	 ;; init for K23~WT  ;; comment
   (-4,0.8,4) 	; THETA(8) POWER volume ~WT    ;;; comment ;; comment
    ;;; comment ;; comment
;; test for comments in blocks
   (-4,.7,4) 	; THETA(9) POWER clearance~WT  
  
   (0.01,0.2) 		;; D1 THETA 
$OMEGA   ;; must be one ETA/line
  0.2  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
$OMEGA
;; test for comments in blocks
  0.2 	; ETA(2) VOLUME
;; optional $OMEGA blocks
$OMEGA ;; 2nd??OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  
;; test for comments in blocks
 
$OMEGA  ;; diagonal OMEGA 
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1
  0.1 		;; ETA(5) ETA ON D1 		;; D1 ETA only 
$SIGMA  
;; test for comments in blocks

  0.3 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  0.3 	; EPS(2) additive error

$COV UNCOND PRINT=E
